deck: Tony Bourne is a comic book writer and author from NYC.
description:
Tony Bourne is a comic-book writer from New York City, New York. However, Bourne has also had many other interesting jobs over the years. He's had prestigious business professions such as as a manager and more low level things such as his time as a bouncer, he was even in the U.S. Army! His most notable comic-book work is probably The Fed book series. Actually The Fed is most likely his only notable comic-book work due to how relatively new to the industry he is at this point. Hopefully he will be able to grow and continue writing/publishing, it's significantly hard to maintain financially stable as an independent/self publisher. Like most comic-book authors, Bourne travels to various comic-book conventions and other festivals to support The Fed and possibly other projects he might be working on.

*Please Note: Tony Bourne does have a twitter account, but for some reason the link doesn't work through this site, so here is a link for the twitter home page, https://twitter.com/ just search for Tony Bourne @BourneCreations. If this link also doesn't work, then there is probably a problem with the site so please report it.
